# Final geometries of predicted structures is generally in 'test.finalensemble.xyz' 
# that can be opened in avogadro2 and visualized along energy/RMSE. 
# Goat is  Global Optimizer Algorithm (GOAT) inspired by 
# Wales and Doye’s basin-hopping, Goedecker’s minima hopping, 
# Simulated Annealing and Taboo Search. 
# Read more at: https://www.faccts.de/docs/orca/6.0/manual/contents/typical/GOAT.html
# Below lines starting with '!' show a test.xyz input file scanned for conformers.
# Goat-react and Goat-explore are further extensions of this tool for reactant to product exploration (react) 
# and conformer search away from the provided structure. 
# This line and above are comments, sample input is below, good to run with 8 parallel processes: 
####################################################
!xtb goat pal8

* xyzfile 0 1 test.xyz
